Function: fromURL()

  fromURL(url, options): Promise<CheerioAPI>

Defined in: src/index.ts:213

fromURL loads a document from a URL.

By default, redirects are allowed and non-2xx responses are rejected.

Parameters

url

The URL to load the document from.

string | URL

options

CheerioRequestOptions = {}

The options to pass to Cheerio.

Returns

Promise<CheerioAPI>

The loaded document.

